mer for a spell</span><hr size=1> I'd set up a social as follows:<br><br>/note #EQATSPELL.START.Nature Skin.00:40:00.00:02:00<br><br>This would set up a timer named 'Nature Skin' with a duration of 40 minutes, and would warn you 2 minutes prior to it expiring that it will be expiring in 120 seconds.  Then after it does expire, it will remind you that it did every 30 seconds to a maximum of 2 reminders.<br><br>to clear it:<br><br>/note #EQATSPELL.STOP.Nature Skin<br><br>or to see how much time you have until it fades, before it does...:<br><br>/note #EQATSPELL.STATUS.Nature Skin<br><br>---<br><br>Socials could be set up for this, or you could manually type it.<br><br>---<br><br>Once you rebuff, or whenever you want to restart the timer...  Just reissue the first command listed above and it will remove the old one out of the timer listing and put your new one in and start it from that point on (effectively resetting it).<br><br>-- Good luck <p><table><tr><td><p><select name="characters" style="font-size: 14; font-family: verdana, arial; color: #80ffff; background-color: black;"><br><option selected>Glimwin Nettlefoot -- 58 Halfling Druid<br><option>Ssytherak Naz'Ghul -- 54 Iksar Necromancer<br><option>Kaelen Nettlefoot -- 51 Halfling Druid<br><option>Braeus Stoneheart -- 49 Dwarf Cleric<br><option>Kaelystia Naz'Ghul -- 41 Dark-Elf Necromancer<br><option>Graakx Gum'Bones -- 35 Troll Warrior<br><option>Ssythlyss Scalefists -- 30 Iksar Monk<br><option>Vaerysla Do'Vrae -- 29 Erudite Enchanter<br><option>Blik Stik -- 28 Halfling Rogue<br></select></p></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub92.ezboard.com/feqannouncefrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=5.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub92.ezboard.com/feqannouncefrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next T